{"tid":1984834,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫情打擊生意；廣州商戶遊行要求減租不果 - 20200421 - 有線中國組","createTime":"2020-04-22T17:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T12:02:57.000Z","uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fd674038caa8449867302d3824733281587cb235","tid":1984834,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T17:24:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BZn3DcvCSvY \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBZn3DcvCSvY%20&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=2bea34b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BZn3DcvCSvY </a><br />\n<br />\n【疫情打擊生意】<br />\n【廣州商戶遊行要求減租不果】<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過百名廣州上涌村商戶周二下午在街道聚集，準備遊行到海珠區政府。不過過了半小時都遲遲未起行。<strong>不久城管到場驅趕，部分戴上紅袖章的人在現場巡邏，之後人群陸續散去，有商戶說是擔心被秋後算帳。</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n自4月中開始，海珠區一帶的城中村，包括上涌村、後滘村、康樂村陸續出現大大小小的遊行示威。參與的都是一些小商戶，他們很多是湖北人，要求區政府寬免2至4月的租金，部分人被警察拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n來自湖北的李先生在村內租屋開了一間小型公寓，主要讓附近工人入住。由2月開始收到居委會通知暫停營業，因此亦無錢交租，至今拖欠房東6萬元租金。他曾找政府幫忙，但對方表示只能協調，不能強制房東免租。<br />\n<br />\n整間公寓有21間房，李先生說平時入住率有八成，不過自3月重新營業以來，入住率大跌到只有一成。<br />\n<br />\n自從商戶開始遊行要求減租之後，不少人都收到房東呼籲不要參加，否則只會被列入黑名單。但參與和政府談判的商戶代表說商討過程並不順利，至今一直未有方案。"},{"pid":"69673977504f4268a95efe7c0518ead5640af275","tid":1984834,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T17:24:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BZn3DcvCSvY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBZn3DcvCSvY&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=2615ca76\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BZn3DcvCSvY</a>"},{"pid":"96e4568e69cd86b0d7d50ba8b745987d0a9314fb","tid":1984834,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T17:25:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>擔心被秋後算帳</strong>  收皮啦支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25af6c43ee90c5e831d4995341d531d1089c225c","tid":1984834,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T17:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b94d1bae653752a33696445566e48be30b8a34e","tid":1984834,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:12:53.000Z","msg":"鄧小平：殺200人保20年穩定<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條撚屌都無撚有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />殺幾十萬人千秋萬世"},{"pid":"3c9e366da857f3cabd10bb02502ab250c207639a","tid":1984834,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />傻閪中國"},{"pid":"7a4203d7559f33591f45e0bf41a7c77e62213616","tid":1984834,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:17:31.000Z","msg":"終國豬你死你事啦<br />\n錢都是我黨員的"},{"pid":"836141799e3348f65960a993663d869a8b410010","tid":1984834,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:21:09.000Z","msg":"冇用嘅<br />\n<br />\n邊屌邊走"},{"pid":"597a5ec3175c97d6bec46030dcdc199f5667127f","tid":1984834,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑鳩佢地先 我地日日出黎示威都有1萬蚊派"},{"pid":"c3400d6d0fbc7e1c980f6f23eea043a230332efc","tid":1984834,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:39:02.000Z","msg":"成班暴徒 收美國錢"},{"pid":"7bd3ae3beb0512cab586ac0f6d1d2801686690ca","tid":1984834,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:48:30.000Z","msg":"這班人就是不相信政府, 政府已經出左消費卷, 點解仲要減租?<br />\n係咪唔相信政府? 係咪收左美國人錢搞事?"},{"pid":"216dca972f3f3f8de3c404a54b7cd73d31b2494c","tid":1984834,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T12:02:57.000Z","msg":"唔明白點解 連登仔 會恥笑廣州人<br />\n<br />\n如果香港人想嬴, 就應該支持大陸每個城市都出現類似 反送中咁既抗爭<br />\n<br />\n到時中共 就會疲於奔命, 日日到處調兵鎮壓, 無時間去搞香港"}]}